FBIS3-59991 "jptdd001__l94033" JPRS-TDD-94-001-L Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Narcotics 3 January 1994 NEAR EAST/SOUTH ASIA PAKISTAN Shabqadar Police Seize 13 Kg of Heroin; Suspect Escapes 94WD0131B Peshawar MASHRIQ in Urdu 12 Nov 93 p 12 94WD0131B Peshawar MASHRIQ Language: Urdu Article Type:CSO [News Report: ``Shabqadar Police Recover 13 Kilograms of Heroin''] [Text] Peshawar (MASHRIQ News) -- The Shabqadar police have recovered 13 kilograms of heroin from an unnamed person; however, he succeeded in running away. According to details, the S.H.O. [Station House Officer] of the Shabqadar police station was making his rounds with his assistants. They saw a man walking with a box in his hand. When he saw the police, he threw the box and ran away. When the box was searched and 13 kilograms of heroin were recovered.
